                <h5>The Future of Death</h5>
                <p>Prompted by Design Boom's Design for Death competition, we spent a week exploring ideas for how we might treat death in the future. With a focus on architecture, we created future designs accomodating for scarcity of land and the abundance of digital information left behind as remains.</p>
